00:14.890 --> 00:19.179
Just... come on. Admit it.
| make a sexy nurse. Hmm?

00:19.228 --> 00:21.139
I can do this. Please.

00:21.188 --> 00:22.803
Okay, then why don't
we just go back in there?

00:22.856 --> 00:24.392
— We can lie down, and...
— (sighs)

